00:50:52,217 --> 00:50:54,469
Sam just makes this such a great...

700
00:50:54,636 --> 00:50:59,474
We have some action, then you come to
the more humanistic things.

701
00:50:59,641 --> 00:51:03,144
It's just so great how he balances
all of that out.

702
00:51:03,353 --> 00:51:05,480
The audience is never scared...

703
00:51:05,647 --> 00:51:09,734
...because right after comes
a happy thing or sweet thing.

704
00:51:09,901 --> 00:51:13,488
It's just a great mixture of action
to the story line.

705
00:51:14,072 --> 00:51:15,490
It just blends very nicely.

706
00:51:15,657 --> 00:51:18,159
Peter, the science award.
That's terrific.

707
00:51:18,576 --> 00:51:19,869
Yeah.

708
00:51:21,162 --> 00:51:23,081
I don't know if I should tell this.

