00:51:34,926 --> 00:51:39,389
So we dressed up the front
of the building...

713
00:51:39,597 --> 00:51:43,101
...and wouldn't let the executives
get into their office on that morning.

714
00:51:43,268 --> 00:51:46,980
I love it. Now when I walk
