738
00:53:26,120 --> 00:53:28,206
You loved him...

739
00:53:29,874 --> 00:53:32,126
...and he loved you.

740
00:53:33,002 --> 00:53:36,631
He never doubted
the man you'd grow into.

741
00:53:36,798 --> 00:53:40,301
How you were meant for great things.

742
00:53:40,802 --> 00:53:43,137
You won't disappoint him.

743
00:54:10,081 --> 00:54:12,291
I love Danny's score right here.

744
00:54:13,668 --> 00:54:16,295
It really takes you into the moment.

