00:54:31,811 --> 00:54:35,982
That shot was shot with an Earl Wiggins
cam in Downtown L.A...

748
00:54:36,149 --> 00:54:38,359
...with a New York background.

749
00:54:39,527 --> 00:54:40,862
Great shot.

