00:55:06,554 --> 00:55:09,557
These guys I actually found
on a construction site.

755
00:55:09,724 --> 00:55:13,853
We were shooting the scene in front
of the library with Uncle Ben...

756
00:55:14,020 --> 00:55:18,191
...and we were trying to get
real faces, great faces.

757
00:55:18,357 --> 00:55:22,195
I found these guys
in this construction site.

758
00:55:23,029 --> 00:55:26,908
