00:55:46,385 --> 00:55:50,056
- He doesn't have Owen's great nose.
- No.

766
00:55:53,100 --> 00:55:56,270
"Who is Spider-Man?"
He's a criminal, that's who he is.

767
00:55:56,437 --> 00:55:59,607
- I love him. He's so good.
- He's fantastic.

768
00:55:59,774 --> 00:56:04,195
J.K. had worked with Sam in The Gift...

769
00:56:04,362 --> 00:56:07,907
...and he came to see us in New York
and it was like meeting you.

770
00:56:08,074 --> 00:56:12,078
It was like, "This guy has to play
this part." Born to play the part.

771
00:56:12,245 --> 00:56:15,122
Once we got the hair...
It's the thing about hair.

772
00:56:15,289 --> 00:56:18,292
Once we got the hair, he was Jameson.

