00:56:46,320 --> 00:56:48,656
Page eight, give him 10 percent off.
Five percent.

782
00:56:48,823 --> 00:56:50,491
- That can't be done.
- Get out!

783
00:56:50,825 --> 00:56:54,453
- He's so good.
- Sam loves to work with him.

784
00:56:54,620 --> 00:56:58,666
It's such a big brother-little brother
