789
00:57:23,232 --> 00:57:26,360
He was in For Love of the <i>Game</i>
but he found the cutting room floor.

790
00:57:26,527 --> 00:57:29,614
But he did a great job for us
in that one too.

791
00:57:29,864 --> 00:57:31,866
Begging for a job. How about you?

792
00:57:32,992 --> 00:57:36,954
Every time I see these two together,
they make a connection for me.

