00:57:37,121 --> 00:57:41,792
She gives a bit of herself in everything
she does. She's very generous.

794
00:57:41,959 --> 00:57:43,502
I just got off a job.

795
00:57:43,669 --> 00:57:47,256
She's great at playing layers
and levels of things.

796
00:57:47,465 --> 00:57:49,842
She's so embarrassed.
Doesn't want Peter to know.

797
00:57:50,009 --> 00:57:52,553
I see she's not a very good liar
in this scene.

798
00:57:53,721 --> 00:57:55,681
Excuse me, Miss Watson?

799
00:57:55,848 --> 00:57:57,558
Busted.

800
00:57:57,725 --> 00:58:00,019
Yes, Enrique! Okay? I get you.

