00:58:06,067 --> 00:58:07,568
He's very empathetic.

804
00:58:08,152 --> 00:58:11,530
- There's the button.
- "Try my cream pie."

805
00:58:13,866 --> 00:58:16,494
It's nothing to be
embarrassed about.

806
00:58:17,203 --> 00:58:21,582
- Makes me want to go to New York.
- Yeah. That was a beautiful day too.

807
00:58:21,791 --> 00:58:24,377
We're going out. Didn't he tell you?

808
00:58:24,877 --> 00:58:26,420
Oh, yeah. Right.

809
00:58:26,754 --> 00:58:29,090
I think he'd hate the idea...

810
00:58:29,298 --> 00:58:30,841
There's paparazzi guys too.

