00:58:31,008 --> 00:58:34,387
Tobey pisses off the paparazzi guys.
They're nicer to me.

812
00:58:34,595 --> 00:58:38,683
- Do they go away when you tell them?
- They're just, like, nicer to me.

813
00:58:39,225 --> 00:58:43,729
The more you act like,
"Don't take my picture," the more...

814
00:58:43,896 --> 00:58:47,024
- Just wave and they go away.
- Give them a moment.

815
00:58:47,191 --> 00:58:51,696
But Tobey likes messing with them
a little bit more.

816
00:58:52,029 --> 00:58:55,241
They were in his eye line.
They stayed out of mine...

817
00:58:55,408 --> 00:59:00,371
...but throughout his eye line they were
always taking his pictures and stuff.

818
00:59:00,538 --> 00:59:04,959
I'll come by and have some of your
Moondance coffee someday.

819
00:59:05,126 --> 00:59:07,795
- And I won't tell Harry.
