01:01:20,719 --> 01:01:23,514
They're very difficult because
Spider-Man can't be doing any...

854
01:01:23,681 --> 01:01:26,600
...of the things in reality
that are needed in these pictures.

855
01:01:26,767 --> 01:01:28,894
We can't do it with an actor.

856
01:01:29,103 --> 01:01:32,773
So we had to stage backgrounds
and separate foreground elements...

857
01:01:32,982 --> 01:01:37,611
...and do a lot of composites
and then clean up in a digital state.

