01:01:56,964 --> 01:02:02,803
...because it signified for me that classic
"girl-in-the-comic-book" kind of look.

864
01:02:03,470 --> 01:02:06,765
I'm pleased about that, that what
we captured looks like a comic book.

865
01:02:06,974 --> 01:02:11,020
Yeah, and it has an old-school
feel to it, the movie, a little bit.

866
01:02:12,313 --> 01:02:16,317
I was so happy that Elizabeth Banks
took the job of Betty Brant...

