01:02:47,514 --> 01:02:51,518
Yeah, he strikes out, but at
the same time, I see on his face...

877
01:02:51,685 --> 01:02:56,482
...that as lame as he is, he's actually
achieved one of his dreams.

878
01:02:56,649 --> 01:02:59,652
- So he feels a sense of fulfillment.
