01:03:02,863 --> 01:03:06,033
...costs are down, revenues are up...

881
01:03:06,867 --> 01:03:09,286
Neil designed this set
on the Warner Bros. lot.

882
01:03:09,453 --> 01:03:14,500
It's one of his best accomplishments,
it's really beautifully detailed.

883
01:03:14,667 --> 01:03:16,460
He created depressions...

884
01:03:16,627 --> 01:03:21,131
...in the walls where
he'd hide these fluorescent tubes.

885
01:03:21,340 --> 01:03:25,469
Quite beautiful, giving it a lot of
dimensionality.

